DBD::PO version 2.01
====================

This is a driver to read/write PO files.
More about PO-Files see module Locale::PO or Locale::Maketext.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    parent
    DBI
    Params::Validate
    Readonly

